            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Silvano <lb n="2"/>libe<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> <expan><abbr>vo</abbr><ex>tum</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>solvit <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Fla</abbr><ex>vius</ex></expan> Luci<lb break="no" n="5"/>anus <expan><abbr>mi</abbr><ex>les</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>le</abbr><ex>gionis</ex></expan> XIIII <expan><abbr>g</abbr><ex>eminae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>artiae</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ictricis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Severia</abbr><ex>nae</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>Ag</abbr><ex>ricola</ex></expan> et <expan><abbr>Cle</abbr><ex>mentino</ex></expan> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Nach Scherrer möglicherweise eine moderne &amp;lt;span style=&amp;apos;color:red&amp;apos;&amp;gt;Fälschung&amp;lt;/span&amp;gt;. Aufbewahrungsort nach lupa 8691. Z. 7 befindet sich auf dem Profil, Z. 8 auf der glatten Vorderseite der crepido.</p>
            </div>
